Date: 19th June, 2024.
Read: - Government Decision Planning Department No. Narrow-2024 / Q. 18 (23) / Q. 1411, D. March 14, 2024.
The Proposal: -
Read about the thematic plan: Ahmedpur Municipal Council and Chakur Nagar Panchayat as per the decision of the Government here.
For Rs. A fund of ₹1 crore has been sanctioned. in the Annexure to this Government Decision.
The local body does not have a clear mention of Ahmedpur Municipal Council and Chakur Nagar Panchayat in front of the sanctioned works.
There is no clarity on the activities within the purview of the autonomous bodies. Therefore, the list of works in this Schedule is hereby deleted.
The approval of the revised list was under the consideration of the government.
The Government's Decisions:
Read above: Withdrawal of the list of works in the Annexure to the Government Decision hereunder:
The revised list is being approved by the government.
